response.overview: Security guard Paul Blart is headed to Las Vegas to attend a Security Guard Expo with his teenage daughter Maya before she departs for college. While at the convention, he inadvertently discovers a heist - and it's up to Blart to apprehend the criminals.
response.tagline: Vegas has a new high roller.
response.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop 2
